1. OVERVIEW
-----------
The AZRAEL_CORE is a "Fail-Operational" logic layer designed to bridge the 
gap between probabilistic AI reasoning and deterministic industrial hardware. 
While standard systems trigger a binary E-Stop (Zero-State) during signal drift, 
the Shepherd Protocol implements Managed Compliance.

2. CORE INNOVATIONS
-------------------
* SIGNAL HARDENING: Multi-modal sensor fusion filtered through an 
  anomaly-weighted moving average to eliminate transient noise.
* IMPEDANCE SCALING: Real-time adjustment of mechanical stiffness ($stiffness$) 
  and damping ($damping$) to absorb system entropy without losing state.
* DETERMINISTIC HEARTBEAT: A 500ms sync window with a 100ms graded response 
  window, ensuring the "Brain" never loses the "Body."

